Instructions for Arch Linux

install powerline-fonts-git
install nvim
install powerline

curl -fLo ~/.local/share/nvim/site/autoload/plug.vim --create-dirs \
    https://raw.githubusercontent.com/junegunn/vim-plug/master/plug.vim

ln -s ~/Projects/vimconfig/.vimrc ~/.config/nvim/init.vim

set konsole to xterm-256color
Settings -> Edit Current Profile... -> Environment: Edit... -> enter "TERM=xterm-256color"
